HEADWORD: Non liquet
<hw>Non` li"quet</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[L.]</ety> <def>It is not
clear; -- a verdict given by a jury when a matter is to be deferred to
another day of trial.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

